  <brief_title>Dexmedetomidine Sedation and Cardiopulmonary Bypass</brief_title>
  <official_title>Dexmedetomidine Based Versus Propofol Based Anesthesia in Patients Undergoing Coronary Revascularization: a Randomized, Double-blind Controlled Study</official_title>
