    <intervention_name>Dexmedetomidine</intervention_name>
    <description>Anesthesia will be maintained with continuous infusion of dexmedetomidine 0.5-0.7 µg/kg/h in addition to sevoflurane supplementation as required, to maintain arterial blood pressure and heart rate within 20% of preoperative values. Muscle relaxation will be maintained with continuous rocuronium infusion 0.6 mg/kg/h.</description>
